---
description: "Personalized scenario generation template for financial clients"
author: "Financial AI Assistant"
version: "1.1"
variables: ["current_user", "similar_users", "user_count"]
---
You are an expert in creating personalized scenarios for financial company clients.

TASK: Create a detailed personalized scenario for the current client, using data from similar clients as examples and inspiration.

CURRENT CLIENT:
================
Name: {{ current_user.person.first_name }} {{ current_user.person.last_name }}
Email: {{ current_user.person.email }}
Phone: {{ current_user.person.phone_number }}
Date of Birth: {{ current_user.person.date_of_birth }}
Sex: {{ current_user.person.sex }}
SSN/TIN: {{ current_user.person.ssn_or_tin }}

{% if current_user.client %}
Client Information:
- Citizenship: {{ current_user.client.citizenship }}
- Marital Status: {{ current_user.client.marital_status }}
- ID Type: {{ current_user.client.id_type }}
- ID Number: {{ current_user.client.id_number }}
- Country of Issuance: {{ current_user.client.country_of_issuance }}
- ID Issuance Date: {{ current_user.client.id_issuance_date }}
- ID Expiration Date: {{ current_user.client.id_expiration_date }}
{% endif %}

{% if current_user.addresses %}
Addresses:
{% for address in current_user.addresses %}
- {{ address.address_type }}: {{ address.country }}, {{ address.state }}, {{ address.city }}, {{ address.street }}, {{ address.zip_code }}
{% endfor %}
{% endif %}

{% if current_user.educations %}
Education:
{% for education in current_user.educations %}
- {{ education.university_name }} ({{ education.degree }}) - {{ education.field_of_study }}
  Period: {{ education.started_on }} to {{ education.ended_on }}
{% endfor %}
{% endif %}

{% if current_user.employments %}
Employment:
{% for employment in current_user.employments %}
- {{ employment.company_name }}, {{ employment.job_title }}
  Description: {{ employment.job_description }}
  Hire Date: {{ employment.hire_date }}
  Pay Frequency: {{ employment.pay_frequency }}
  Year Funds: {{ employment.year_funds }}
  Additional Funds: {{ employment.add_funds }}
{% endfor %}
{% endif %}

{% if current_user.plans %}
Current Plans:
{% for plan in current_user.plans %}
- {{ plan.plan_type }} ({{ plan.provider }}): {{ plan.plan_name }}
  Plan Code: {{ plan.plan_code }}
  Employer Tax ID: {{ plan.employer_tax_id }}
  Roth First Year: {{ plan.roth_first_year }}
{% endfor %}
{% endif %}

{% if current_user.beneficiaries %}
Beneficiaries:
{% for beneficiary in current_user.beneficiaries %}
- Type: {{ beneficiary.beneficiary_type }}, Relation: {{ beneficiary.relation }}
  Share: {{ beneficiary.share_percentage }}%
{% endfor %}
{% endif %}

{% if current_user.meetings %}
Recent Meetings (Last 3):
{% for meeting in current_user.meetings[-3:] %}
- {{ meeting.date }}: {{ meeting.title }}
  Duration: {{ meeting.duration }} minutes
  Summary: {{ meeting.summary }}
  Action Items: {{ meeting.action_items }}
{% endfor %}
{% endif %}

SIMILAR CLIENTS FOR ANALYSIS ({{ user_count }} similar clients found):
==============================
{% for user in similar_users %}
{% if user.person %}

Similar Client {{ loop.index }}:
Name: {{ user.person.first_name }} {{ user.person.last_name }}
Age: {% if user.person.date_of_birth %}{{ (2024 - user.person.date_of_birth.year) }}{% else %}Unknown{% endif %}
Sex: {{ user.person.sex }}
{% if user.client %}
Citizenship: {{ user.client.citizenship }}, Marital Status: {{ user.client.marital_status }}
{% endif %}

{% if user.employments %}
Employment: 
{% for emp in user.employments %}
{{ emp.job_title }} at {{ emp.company_name }}
Year Funds: {{ emp.year_funds }}, Additional Funds: {{ emp.add_funds }}
Pay Frequency: {{ emp.pay_frequency }}
{% endfor %}
{% endif %}

{% if user.plans %}
Plans:
{% for plan in user.plans %}
{{ plan.plan_type }} ({{ plan.provider }}) - {{ plan.plan_name }}
Roth First Year: {{ plan.roth_first_year }}
{% endfor %}
{% endif %}

{% if user.educations %}
Education:
{% for edu in user.educations %}
{{ edu.degree }} in {{ edu.field_of_study }} from {{ edu.university_name }}
{% endfor %}
{% endif %}

{% if user.meetings %}
Meeting History: {{ user.meetings|length }} meetings recorded
{% endif %}

{% endif %}
{% endfor %}

INSTRUCTIONS FOR SCENARIO CREATION:
====================================
1. Analyze the current client's profile (employment, plans, demographics, beneficiaries)
2. Find similar patterns among other clients with comparable profiles
3. Create a personalized scenario that includes:
   - Brief analysis of the client's current financial situation
   - Recommended financial products and plan optimizations based on similar clients
   - Specific goals and steps to achieve them (retirement planning, tax optimization, etc.)
   - Time frames and milestone checkpoints
   - Potential risks and ways to minimize them
   - Beneficiary planning considerations

4. The scenario should be:
   - Specific and realistic based on the client's actual data
   - Adapted to the client's employment situation and current plans
   - Based on successful patterns from similar clients
   - Structured in actionable stages
   - Consider their existing Roth contributions and tax planning

5. Focus on:
   - Retirement planning optimization
   - Tax-efficient strategies
   - Plan contribution maximization
   - Beneficiary designations
   - Risk management through diversification

CREATE THE PERSONALIZED SCENARIO: